	</div>
	<div class="withinContainer">
		<div class="homeFeatureItemDetail homeFeatureFontDark">
			<h4>
				Transforming Tobacco</h4>
			<div class="homeFeatureItemContent">
				<p>
					We have a clear ambition to lead the transformation of our industry by offering adult consumers a range of potentially reduced-risk products.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="homeFeatureItemLink">
				<a  class="link" href="/group/sites/UK__9D9KCY.nsf/vwPagesWebLive/DO52ADCY" title="Who we are - Transforming tobacco">Who we are &ndash; Transforming Tobacco</a> <i aria-hidden="true" class="icon-arrow"></i></div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
