					<div class="contentSpotText">
						<h4>
							New products, more choices</h4>
						<p class="contentSpotContent">
							Our product portfolio is growing as we extend our range with vapour, tobacco heating and oral tobacco and nicotine products.</p>
						<p class="contentSpotLink">
							<a  class="link" href="/group/sites/UK__9D9KCY.nsf/vwPagesWebLive/DOAWUGND"  title="Potentially reduced risk products">Potentially reduced-risk products</a><i aria-hidden="true" class="icon-arrow"></i></p>
