					<div class="contentSpotText">
						<h4>
							We&rsquo;re growing together</h4>
						<p class="contentSpotContent">
							We are committed to working to enable prosperous livelihoods for all farmers who supply our tobacco leaf.</p>
						<p class="contentSpotLink">
							<a  class="link" href="/group/sites/UK__9D9KCY.nsf/vwPagesWebLive/DO52APTT"  title="A sustainable approach">Sustainable agriculture and farmer livelihoods</a><i aria-hidden="true" class="icon-arrow"></i></p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
