				See our world through the eyes of people who work for and with us.</h4>
			<p>
				<a  class="link" href="/group/sites/UK__9D9KCY.nsf/vwPagesWebLive/DO6ZXMRV" title="We are BAT">Watch the video</a><i aria-hidden="true" class="icon-arrow"></i></p>
